          <details>
            <summary>PC won't boot — black screen</summary>
            <p class="small">Check power connections, ensure CPU power and 24-pin motherboard power are connected, reseat RAM, and try the motherboard speaker for beep codes.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>System unstable / random reboots</summary>
            <p class="small">Test with one stick of RAM, check PSU wattage vs GPU requirements, monitor temperatures, and update BIOS if needed.</p>
          </details>
